<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM4.2.2">
<l>vallā ḷaṉtōḷum vāḷarak kaṉmuṭi yuntaṅkai</l>
<l>pollā tamūkkum pōkkuvit tāṉporun tummalai</l>
<l>yellā viṭattilu meṅkum parantupal lāṇṭoli</l>
<l>cellā niṟkumcīrt teṉtiru māliruñ cōlaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The mountain where dwells</l>
<l rend="indent">he who cut off the arms of the strong one,</l>
<l rend="indent">the heads of the sword[-bearing] demon,</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] the nose of the evil younger sister,</l>
<l>is Tirumāliruñcōlai in the South of spreading fame,</l>
<l rend="indent">where “Many years” resounds,</l>
<l rend="indent">pervading everywhere, in every place.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
